Our wheat trade
is in the black by

00:09:51.959 --> 00:09:53.928 position:5% line:89% align:start
fourteen silver and five copper.

00:09:54.061 --> 00:09:56.864 position:19% line:83% align:start
And if you account for
the emergency aid we received,

00:09:58.199 --> 00:10:00.401 position:10% line:83% align:start
that's four and three-eighths
gold profit.

00:10:00.535 --> 00:10:03.170 position:30% line:83% align:start
There's the end
of last year's earnings report!

00:10:03.704 --> 00:10:05.106 position:27% line:89% align:start
Congratulations!

00:10:05.239 --> 00:10:07.675 position:5% line:83% align:start
Our administration has succeeded
in staying within budget

00:10:07.808 --> 00:10:09.910 position:24% line:83% align:start
and has even earned
a full-year profit!

00:10:10.044 --> 00:10:13.047 position:33% line:83% align:start
At long last
we've come to this point.

00:10:13.814 --> 00:10:15.850 position:16% line:83% align:start
I've always tried to look
at the bright side,

00:10:15.983 --> 00:10:18.752 position:19% line:83% align:start
but it was pretty touch
and go when we first got here.

00:10:19.920 --> 00:10:21.655 position:19% line:89% align:start
The past twenty years,

00:10:22.690 --> 00:10:28.129 position:7% line:83% align:start
it's had its ups and its downs,
but it all paid off.

00:10:28.929 --> 00:10:31.966 position:16% line:83% align:start
It sure has and the boy's
been a big help, hasn't he?

00:10:32.099 --> 00:10:34.503 position:16% line:89% align:start
My dear son! What a gift!

00:10:34.635 --> 00:10:37.805 position:13% line:83% align:start
He must've been sent by God
to answer my prayers.

00:10:37.938 --> 00:10:39.907 position:19% line:83% align:start
I wasn't gonna take it
quite that far.

00:10:40.040 --> 00:10:42.910 position:7% line:89% align:start
Look at you, what a proud papa!

00:10:43.043 --> 00:10:44.011 position:38% line:89% align:start
Feuille,

00:10:45.146 --> 00:10:46.747 position:13% line:89% align:start
you've done so much for me.

00:10:46.881 --> 00:10:48.182 position:21% line:89% align:start
Throughout everything

00:10:48.315 --> 00:10:50.784 position:13% line:83% align:start
you, Cointreau and Glacage
stayed with me.

00:10:50.918 --> 00:10:52.386 position:30% line:89% align:start
I owe you all.

00:10:52.521 --> 00:10:54.088 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh, give me a break.

00:10:54.221 --> 00:10:57.258 position:10% line:83% align:start
I made the decision to stick
with you a long time ago,

00:10:57.391 --> 00:10:58.926 position:16% line:89% align:start
so don't worry about it.

00:10:59.059 --> 00:11:02.863 position:10% line:83% align:start
Now, there are two remaining
updates that I'm here to report.

00:11:02.997 --> 00:11:06.033 position:5% line:83% align:start
Which do you want to hear first?
The good news or the bad?

00:11:06.500 --> 00:11:10.171 position:19% line:83% align:start
Let me see. Let's start
with the good news.

00:11:10.304 --> 00:11:11.372 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm feeling lucky.

00:11:11.506 --> 00:11:13.774 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'd like to hold on
to that for a while.

00:11:13.908 --> 00:11:15.943 position:35% line:83% align:start
That's what
I figured you would say.

00:11:16.744 --> 00:11:18.012 position:19% line:89% align:start
You're gonna like this.

00:11:18.145 --> 00:11:20.114 position:30% line:83% align:start
We've gathered
over forty applicants

00:11:20.247 --> 00:11:23.450 position:21% line:83% align:start
who want to move into
our new village, Le Milotte.

00:11:23.951 --> 00:11:25.386 position:35% line:83% align:start
[CASSEROLE]
Wow, forty people?

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:28.689 position:27% line:83% align:start
Most of them are
refugees from nearby.

00:11:28.822 --> 00:11:30.191 position:30% line:83% align:start
