with nowhere to go

00:11:30.324 --> 00:11:33.260 position:19% line:83% align:start
after their farms were
ravaged by bandits.

00:11:33.994 --> 00:11:35.462 position:13% line:89% align:start
If there are forty of them,

00:11:35.597 --> 00:11:37.865 position:7% line:83% align:start
we'll want to speed up getting
the village in shape.

00:11:38.567 --> 00:11:40.901 position:13% line:83% align:start
[FEUILLE] Well, we do have
more manpower now.

00:11:41.035 --> 00:11:42.436 position:5% line:89% align:start
So, I think we'll figure it out.

00:11:42.571 --> 00:11:45.039 position:24% line:83% align:start
And how have those
newcomers been doing?

00:11:45.172 --> 00:11:47.308 position:19% line:83% align:start
You mean, the five men
we hired with the money

00:11:47.441 --> 00:11:49.743 position:21% line:83% align:start
we got from handling
the Licorice kidnapping?

00:11:50.311 --> 00:11:52.780 position:41% line:83% align:start
Glacage
is showing them the ropes.

00:11:53.881 --> 00:11:55.149 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's good.

00:11:55.282 --> 00:11:56.984 position:27% line:83% align:start
So long as having
more people means

00:11:57.117 --> 00:12:00.421 position:19% line:83% align:start
the land will grow more
prosperous, I won't complain.

00:12:00.888 --> 00:12:03.724 position:7% line:89% align:start
So, what is the bad news about?

00:12:03.857 --> 00:12:05.793 position:19% line:89% align:start
So, this is a big one.

00:12:06.595 --> 00:12:08.062 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's your kid.

00:12:08.195 --> 00:12:10.532 position:10% line:83% align:start
I've been told he's embarked
in a brand-new venture.

00:12:11.732 --> 00:12:14.502 position:13% line:83% align:start
Someone sent a report that
he was headed all the way out

00:12:14.636 --> 00:12:17.871 position:19% line:83% align:start
to Le Milotte with just
his two friends in tow.

00:12:18.005 --> 00:12:20.107 position:13% line:89% align:start
That little mischief-maker!

00:12:20.241 --> 00:12:22.943 position:19% line:83% align:start
Why can't he sit still
for a single minute?

00:12:23.077 --> 00:12:25.980 position:10% line:89% align:start
[thuds] Feuille, we're going!

00:12:26.113 --> 00:12:27.915 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm ready when you are!

00:12:37.958 --> 00:12:39.760 position:35% line:89% align:start
[BOTH sigh]

00:12:41.028 --> 00:12:44.999 position:16% line:89% align:start
[crackles] Let's do this.

00:12:48.769 --> 00:12:50.804 position:27% line:89% align:start
Time to Excavate!

00:12:52.973 --> 00:12:55.242 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:12:56.711 --> 00:12:59.413 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ALL groan]

00:13:02.416 --> 00:13:04.351 position:35% line:89% align:start
[BOTH gasp]

00:13:06.320 --> 00:13:07.656 position:27% line:89% align:start
What did you do?

00:13:07.788 --> 00:13:09.290 position:38% line:89% align:start
Awesome!

00:13:10.224 --> 00:13:11.292 position:38% line:89% align:start
Amazing.

00:13:12.459 --> 00:13:14.928 position:21% line:83% align:start
[PAS] I can't believe
I was able to secretly replicate

00:13:15.062 --> 00:13:17.164 position:10% line:89% align:start
Strudel's magic so perfectly!

00:13:18.667 --> 00:13:20.801 position:19% line:89% align:start
That was so crazy, Pas!

00:13:20.934 --> 00:13:23.103 position:16% line:89% align:start
Magic, right? What kind?

00:13:23.871 --> 00:13:25.039 position:47% line:89% align:start
Uh!

00:13:25.172 --> 00:13:27.941 position:41% line:83% align:start
[BOTH]
Um, Pas? Are you...

00:13:28.075 --> 00:13:31.278 position:38% line:83% align:start
[laughs]
It worked? This is great!

00:13:31.412 --> 00:13:34.683 position:5% line:83% align:start
And this spell's way more useful
than I expected it to be!

00:13:34.815 --> 00:13:36.651 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:13:36.785 --> 00:13:40.220 position:30% line:83% align:start
I can do this!
I feel so powerful right now!

00:13:40.354 --> 00:13:42.189 position:13% line:89% align:start
It will work! It will work!

00:13:42.323 --> 00:13:44.793 position:10% line:83% align:start
-It will work! It will work!
-Did he crack?

00:13:44.925 --> 00:13:47.194 position:19% line:83% align:start
Our next suzerain lord
has gone mad.

00:13:47.895 --> 00:13:50.364 position:38% line:83% align:start
Now then,
let's move on to the next one!

00:13:50.497 --> 00:13:51.733 position:38% line:89% align:start
Excavate!

00:13:51.865 --> 00:13:53.735 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:13:53.867 --> 00:13:54.868 position:38% line:89% align:start
Excavate!

00:13:55.002 --> 00:13:56.738 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:13:56.870 --> 00:13:59.808 position:10% line:89% align:start
