00:13:59.940 --> 00:14:03.778 position:24% line:89% align:start
Excavate! Excavate!

00:14:03.911 --> 00:14:05.412 position:35% line:89% align:start
[BOTH sigh]

00:14:05.547 --> 00:14:08.015 position:33% line:89% align:start
Huh! [laughs]

00:14:08.148 --> 00:14:09.718 position:16% line:89% align:start
That should about do it!

00:14:09.850 --> 00:14:11.051 position:24% line:89% align:start
I can't believe it!

00:14:11.185 --> 00:14:14.288 position:30% line:83% align:start
