really hard.

00:14:19.993 --> 00:14:21.830 position:16% line:89% align:start
Because it's a reservoir!

00:14:21.962 --> 00:14:23.364 position:21% line:89% align:start
Here's what I think.

00:14:23.497 --> 00:14:25.667 position:10% line:83% align:start
We should go ahead and plant
the trees all around it.

00:14:25.800 --> 00:14:28.837 position:7% line:83% align:start
It shouldn't be too long before
it rains again,

00:14:28.969 --> 00:14:30.371 position:16% line:89% align:start
