00:14:31.271 --> 00:14:35.175 position:24% line:83% align:start
As the trees grow,
they'll store their own water,

00:14:35.309 --> 00:14:38.178 position:33% line:83% align:start
thus creating
a symbiotic relationship

00:14:38.312 --> 00:14:40.948 position:19% line:83% align:start
[PAS] that'll all work
together in harmony!

00:14:42.015 --> 00:14:44.118 position:13% line:89% align:start
Uh! What a dream come true!

00:14:44.251 --> 00:14:45.687 position:35% line:83% align:start
