00:15:03.337 --> 00:15:06.608 position:13% line:83% align:start
Yeah, well, you might wanna
consider opening those eyes now.

00:15:06.741 --> 00:15:11.178 position:13% line:83% align:start
No way. I'm really enjoying
myself. Why would I wanna...

00:15:14.749 --> 00:15:16.016 position:47% line:89% align:start
Uh!

00:15:16.150 --> 00:15:18.620 position:24% line:83% align:start
