00:15:46.480 --> 00:15:48.650 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ALL scream]

00:15:50.250 --> 00:15:52.787 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Urgh!
-That hurt bad!

00:15:52.921 --> 00:15:55.189 position:10% line:89% align:start
Why'd you have to hit us too?

00:15:56.256 --> 00:15:58.258 position:38% line:83% align:start
[COATON]
